    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="该如何想让小说封面显示标题呢？" class="article-title">
          该如何想让小说封面显示标题呢？
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>在小说投稿画面中，通过选择并设置封面模板，即可在封面中显示出标题。<br>APP版及自定义封面不支持该功能。</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3>想使用自己上传的图片时</h3>
<p>请参考以下帮助。<br><a href="https://www.pixiv.help/hc/ja/articles/235584208-%E5%B0%8F%E8%AA%AC%E3%81%AE%E8%A1%A8%E7%B4%99%E3%82%92%E8%87%AA%E4%BD%9C%E3%81%AE%E3%82%A4%E3%83%A9%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E3%81%AB%E3%81%A7%E3%81%8D%E3%81%BE%E3%81%99%E3%81%8B-" target="_self" rel="undefined">小说封面可以使用自己画的图吗？</a></p>
<p><br><a href="#h_01EECHQ4Y5MJSJJ08TJR91P08V" target="_self" rel="undefined">▶︎电脑版</a><br><a href="#h_01EECHQHEM5214P02N1DF1Z5DW" target="_self" rel="undefined">▶︎手机版</a><br><a href="#h_01EKF3ZV48VV5H3Y82C3MH5G8K" target="_self">▶APP版</a></p>
<h3 id="h_01EECHQ4Y5MJSJJ08TJR91P08V">电脑版</h3>
<p>请在列表中选择喜欢的封面模板。</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002672386/mceclip0.png" alt="mceclip0.png" width="735" height="422"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>点选「查看全部」即可开启所有封面模板列表。</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002672726/mceclip5.png" alt="mceclip5.png"></p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/8938421234457/___________182_.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/8938421234457/___________182_.png" alt="___________182_.png"></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>选择后即可在「设置封面」中编辑想显示的标题。<br>请点选「封面预览」右侧的「设置封面」。<br><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002672426/mceclip2.png" alt="mceclip2.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>设置封面中可调整「是否显示标题」「显示内容」「字体」与「文字颜色」。</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002672466/mceclip3.png" alt="mceclip3.png"></p>
<h4>&nbsp;</h4>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01EECHQHEM5214P02N1DF1Z5DW">手机版</h3>
<p>请在列表中选择喜欢的封面模板。</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002652123/mceclip6.png" alt="mceclip6.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>点选「查看全部」即可开启所有封面模板列表。</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002652163/mceclip7.png" alt="mceclip7.png"></p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/8938494368665/___________183_.png" alt="___________183_.png" width="444" height="582"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>选择后即可在「设置封面」中编辑想显示的标题。<br>请点选「封面预览」右侧的「设置封面」。<br><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002674466/mceclip9.png" alt="mceclip9.png"></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>设置封面中可调整「是否显示标题」「显示内容」「字体」与「文字颜色」。</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/900002652283/mceclip10.png" alt="mceclip10.png"></p>
<h4>&nbsp;</h4>
<h3 id="h_01EKF3ZV48VV5H3Y82C3MH5G8K">▶APP版</h3>
<p>APP版尚不支持编辑封面标题。<br>同时，即使通过APP版设置封面，也无法再通过电脑版或手机版设置封面标题。</p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

